com.github.naoghuman.lib.tag.core

Interface TagBuilder.Step

  • Enclosing class:
    TagBuilder

    public static interface TagBuilder.Step
    Optional steps for the configuration from the new instance from the Interface Tag.
    • All attributes in this Interface are optional. If not set, then Optional.empty() will be returned.
    • All setted values will be validate against the Interface DefaultTagValidator.
    • For any optinal attribute if setted more then ones then the last value will be used for the configuration.
    Since:
    0.1.0
    Version:
    0.4.0
    See Also:
    DefaultTagValidator, Optional.empty()
